    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for throughout its life. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior remains in pristine condition, still smelling like new. Mechanically, it is perfect, with all maintenance records up to date and no signs of wear. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a car that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
