    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in a vehicle that\u2019s full of character and ready for its next chapter! This car has been a dependable companion and still has plenty of life left for your daily commutes or weekend errands. While it shows some honest signs of its journey and could use a little TLC to shine its brightest, it remains a solid choice for anyone seeking reliable transportation at a great value!",
