    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen in truly immaculate condition. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation, featuring a flawless exterior finish complemented by a pristine, showroom-quality interior. Meticulously maintained and rigorously inspected, it offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning enthusiast. We invite you to acquire a vehicle that defies its age and stands as a definitive testament to superior ownership.",
      "price": 46500.0,
